@NEXT "ReportLevel0"

   These menu items will set the Level of result reporting in the Status
   window.  These menuitems set an internal flag named @{" prntcmd " LINK "Appendix_2/LINE 33"}.
   
   SEE ALSO, @{" Level 0 " LINK "ReportLevel0"},
             @{" Level 1 " LINK "ReportLevel1"},@{" Level 2 " LINK "ReportLevel2"} 
