@NODE "ReportLevel0" "Display Requested Results only! (PRNTCMD=0):"
@PREV "ReportLevel"
@NEXT "ReportLevel1"

   When this menu item is checked, the only results displayed in the status
   window will be from explicit print messages.
   
   SEE ALSO, @{" Level 1 " LINK "ReportLevel1"},@{" Level 2 " LINK "ReportLevel2"} 
@ENDNODE

@NODE "ReportLevel1" "Display Results of Expressions (Default):"
@PREV "ReportLevel0"
