   When this menu item is checked, the results of every expression typed in the
   Command String Gadget will be displayed in the status window.
   
   SEE ALSO, @{" Level 0 " LINK "ReportLevel0"},@{" Level 2 " LINK "ReportLevel2"} 
@ENDNODE

@NODE "ReportLevel2" "Display ALL Results! (PRNTCMD=2):"
@PREV "ReportLevel1"
